{"tid":582844,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過日久生情:~(","createTime":"2018-03-06T13:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T11:01:17.000Z","uid":80183,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"15c160c1424efc6104f84d8c08706d705342bae9","tid":582844,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:32:05.000Z","msg":"開頭都唔係好鐘意條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢搵親我都想快close topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係條女都係隔一排搵番我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢我就覺得個女仔好似幾好咁<br />\n係我最失意時陪住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尼幾日佢冇搵我搞到我心掛掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知佢好快要走<br />\n我唔知我係米真係鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我知我唔捨得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想攬住佢坐係海邊睇日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774f02d788711d7a279f861af0d5d12a481f270e","tid":582844,"uid":173208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"a09!"},{"pid":"5b8de878fda69c7cea9717a4edb2a38c67e3d387","tid":582844,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774f02d788711d7a279f861af0d5d12a481f270e","tid":582844,"uid":173208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"a09!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8498b1debc47889e8677856b3acfe971d11fc6","tid":582844,"uid":173208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b8de878fda69c7cea9717a4edb2a38c67e3d387","tid":582844,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774f02d788711d7a279f861af0d5d12a481f